      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/quebec-premier-talks-with-trump-and-musk-on-trade-and-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[魁北克省省长弗朗索瓦·勒戈特 (Francois Legault) 周六在巴黎出席巴黎圣母院重新开放仪式期间与当选总统唐纳德·特朗普讨论了边境管制和关税问题。]]></description>
